## Quick Reference: Key Formulas

### Survival Probability
```
Q(t) = exp[-λ₀ t - (λ₁/β)(1 - exp(-βt))]
```

### Default Probability
```
PD(t) = 1 - Q(t)
```

### Bullet Bond Price
```
P = Σ (coupon × B(t) × Q(t)) + 100 × B(T) × Q(T) + Recovery × ExpectedLoss
```

### Callable Bond Price
```
P = Value from tree pricing
    (accounts for optimal call decisions at each node)
```

### Risky PV01
```
Π(T) = ∫₀ᵀ B(t)Q(t)dt
```

### Expected Loss
```
Ξ(T) = ∫₀ᵀ B(t)dQ(t)
```

